Our independence gives us the freedom to deliver the best solutions for our clients.

Howden Specialty is the largest producer of direct premium to Lloyd’s, the world’s leading specialist insurance market, and a leading producer to many of the world’s largest specialist insurers.

GLOBAL BUSINESS
BOUTIQUE OUTLOOK

As the nature of risk evolves, so do our lines of business. We cover the full range of insurance and reinsurance broking specialisms, with access to an extensive retail network. We are located in the world’s key insurance markets and serve clients in 130 territories around the globe.

TECNOLOGY
& INNOVATION

We use data and technology to enable the efficient and effective distribution of the right products to our clients at the right price. Our capability to design, development and deliver insurtech solutions in-house not only creates opportunities to enhance products and service to existing clients, but allows us to use technology as a gateway to new market spaces.
